    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个《Slidezzle》关卡都带来独特的挑战，需要玩家仔细思考并规划移动步骤，以达成最终目标。你的任务是将彩色方块滑动至指定的位置，所有方块会同时朝相同方向移动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129170/extras/f7dd841b6a7cb502a8b4608fbe14d0ed.poster.avif?t=1745605289\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129170/extras/f7dd841b6a7cb502a8b4608fbe14d0ed.webm?t=1745605289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129170/extras/f7dd841b6a7cb502a8b4608fbe14d0ed.mp4?t=1745605289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些方块只是为了帮助其他方块，这使得解谜过程需要精确的策略与计划。请善用这些方块来解开每个谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129170/extras/ae58944910b6e809cbf3409c8b3abb21.poster.avif?t=1745605289\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129170/extras/ae58944910b6e809cbf3409c8b3abb21.webm?t=1745605289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129170/extras/ae58944910b6e809cbf3409c8b3abb21.mp4?t=1745605289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏设计为无压力、无负担的体验——没有广告、没有时间限制，也没有分数。如果卡关了，不用担心！你可以按下“重玩”按钮，重新挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内共有 72 道精心设计的谜题，每一关都带来新的概念，让你享受解谜的乐趣，没有任何冗余内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可使用鼠标或键盘进行游玩。</p>",
